1970;;Every Home Should Have One;;British;;Jim Clark;;Marty Feldman, Judy Cornwell;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Every_Home_Should_Have_One;;An advertising man is asked by his boss to try to come up with a sexy new image for porridge. He is also struggling with his chaotic home life, where his wife has become involved in a campaign to "clean up" television.[3]